result:
<a-modal
  :visible="visible"
  :keyboard="false"
  :maskClosable="false"
  okText="保存"
  okType="primary"
  @ok="handleOk()"
  @cancel="handleCancel()">
  <a-form
    :form="form">
    <a-form-item
      label="计划花费："
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        addonAfter="元"
        v-decorator="[
        'allPaidTotal',
        {
          rules: [
            { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
          ],
          validateTrigger: 'blur',
          initialValue: card ? card.allPaidTotal : null
        }
      ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
  </a-form>
</a-modal>
